{"word":"λιθουργός","slug":"λιθουργός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>λιθουργός</b></el> <el>(λῐθ-ουργός, οῦ, ὁ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>*<a href='S:ἔργω'><el>ἔργω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a worker in stone, stone-mason</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b>as <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a>, <el>σιδήρια λιθουργά</el> a <i>stonemason's</i> tools, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}